Description: A decadently creamy concoction crafted from raw eggs, thick cream, honey, and─if you are feeling adventurous─a healthy splash of a dark spiced rum. A favorite in Ishgard's Vault. EXP Bonus: +3% Duration: 30m (Duration can be extended to 60m by consuming multiple servings)

Name: Spaghetti Pescatore

Description: While similar to a regular omelette, this recipe perfected in the Vault's kitchens calls for a fistful of shredded cheese and mushrooms to further enhance the dish's richness. EXP Bonus: +3% Duration: 30m (Duration can be extended to 60m by consuming multiple servings)
